  "french-defense/advance-french/line-1": "This Advance French line features a specific pawn break timing that defines the middlegame. The key lesson: in closed positions, piece maneuvering and pawn breaks must be carefully coordinated. Don't rush your breaks — prepare them with piece placement first.",
