  "caro-kann/classical-ck/line-0": "The Classical Caro-Kann leads to solid, strategic positions. After developing the bishop to f5 (or g6), Black has a reliable structure. White should aim for a space advantage and piece activity. This opening teaches the value of sound pawn structure and patient play.",
