  "ruy-lopez/morphy-defense/line-0": "The Ruy Lopez Morphy Defense is one of the most important openings in chess history. The main line leads to a rich middlegame with strategic depth. White's plan involves the Marshall Attack or the Breyer/Chigorin maneuvers. Mastering this opening is essential for any serious player.",
