  "london-system/london-classical/line-0": "The London System is one of the most reliable openings for White. The classical setup with Bf4, e3, and Nbd2 leads to a solid position with clear plans. Focus on the c4 break or a kingside expansion with h3 and g4 in appropriate positions.",
